<div class='commentbox'>
you can simplify your shuttle, if you have a high clearance 4 wheel drive vehicle and a bike by<br/>
using the south bank rd (which has three different names; Copco Lake Rd., Ager Beswick Rd.. Topsy<br/>
Grade Rd.) By google mapping Copco Lake Rd. you'll see where to go. Some people (including me) find<br/>
using this access a bit unnerving as you'll be putting in right above Caldera with no warm-up. But<br/>
it relieves the need for a shuttle driver and cuts shuttle time by hours. </div>
